OL,3,C'He's ruined any trust I have with
OL,4,Cpolice': Calls for better protection
OL,6,FA survivor of domestic abuse, who was
OL,7,Ftaken advantage of by a police officer
OL,8,Fwho was sent to help her, is calling
OL,9,Ffor better protection for women.
OL,11,FShannon Mulhall, who has waived her
OL,12,Fright to anonymity, has spoken to ITV
OL,13,FCalendar in the hopes of helping more
OL,14,Fpeople like her.
OL,16,FIn 2021, Shannon Mulhall was at her
OL,17,Flowest. Having just escaped an abusive
OL,18,Frelationship and feeling suicidal, she
OL,19,Fcalled the police for help.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
