OL,3,C'He's ruined any trust I have with
OL,4,Cpolice': Calls for better protection
OL,6,F"I went in the living room to grab my
OL,7,Fbag and, as I came back out, he was
OL,8,Falready naked. He was completely
OL,9,Fnaked."
OL,11,F"I was like, 'What are you doing?
OL,12,FWhat's going on?' And he started
OL,13,Fapproaching me. I just didn't know
OL,14,Fwhat to do; I just froze. (...) I was
OL,15,Fliterally powerless against him."
OL,17,FHe then turned off his police radio
OL,18,Fand camera and had sex with her.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@GO]vD@[pmvD@_pn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/12
