OL,3,C'He's ruined any trust I have with
OL,4,Cpolice': Calls for better protection
OL,6,FHull Crown Court heard he later told
OL,7,Fher if she reported him"they won't
OL,8,Fbelieve you because you are in a
OL,9,Fmental asylum".
OL,11,F"I am still living with nightmares; I
OL,12,Fam still living with panic attacks. I
OL,13,Fam scared of leaving home in case I
OL,14,Fbump into him. He could be anywhere."
OL,15,FMs. Mulhall said.
OL,17,F"He's ruined any trust I've got with
OL,18,Fany police."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/12
