OL,3,C'He's ruined any trust I have with
OL,4,Cpolice': Calls for better protection
OL,6,FMiller, 54, of Scunthorpe, had
OL,7,Fadmitted misusing police powers by
OL,8,Fhaving a sexual relationship with a
OL,9,Fvictim, knowing it was improper.
OL,11,FIn November 2023, Miller was jailed
OL,12,Ffor two years and four months. He had
OL,13,Falready been sacked by Humberside
OL,14,FPolice and was placed on the College
OL,15,Fof Policing Barred List.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
