OL,3,C'He's ruined any trust I have with
OL,4,Cpolice': Calls for better protection
OL,6,FAt the time of his sentencing,
OL,7,FHumberside Police described Simon
OL,8,FMiller's actions as "utterly
OL,9,Freprehensible," stating that such
OL,10,Fbehaviour "undermines public
OL,11,Fconfidence in Humberside Police and
OL,12,Fbrings the entire profession into
OL,13,Fdisrepute."
OL,15,FThe force further encouraged anyone
OL,16,Fwho believes they have been a victim
OL,17,Fof similar offences to come forward
OL,18,Fand report them.
OL,26,@pD@UOUqD@OO]rD@KOUuD@KO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/12
