OL,3,C'He's ruined any trust I have with
OL,4,Cpolice': Calls for better protection
OL,6,FAcross the five forces in the Calendar
OL,7,Fregion, since 2021 there have been 47
OL,8,Freferrals to the Independent Office
OL,9,Ffor Police Conduct regarding abuse of
OL,10,Fpower for a sexual purpose.
OL,12,FFor England and Wales, that figure
OL,13,Frises to nearly five hundred cases -
OL,14,Fapproximately 100 a year.
OL,16,FShannon's lawyer, Kevin Donoghue, who
OL,17,Fspecialises in police misconduct
OL,18,Fcases, said: "I have been practicing
OL,19,Ffor 25 years. There is a significant
OL,20,Famount of cases coming forward like
OL,21,Fthis, which I say is extremely sad."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
