OL,3,C'He's ruined any trust I have with
OL,4,Cpolice': Calls for better protection
OL,6,FHe added: "It simply shouldn't happen
OL,7,Fin this modern age, where we can
OL,8,Futilise modern technology, vetting can
OL,9,Fbe done a lot better and despite all
OL,10,Fof that we still have these high
OL,11,Fnumbers of reports."
OL,13,FIn March 2021, Sarah Everard was
OL,14,Fmurdered and raped by, then serving
OL,15,FMetropolitan police officer, Wayne
OL,16,FCouzens. Her murder sent shockwaves
OL,17,Fthrough the nation sparking a crisis
OL,18,Fof confidence in policing.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
