OL,3,C'He's ruined any trust I have with
OL,4,Cpolice': Calls for better protection
OL,6,FMs. Mulhall heard of Sarah's murder
OL,7,Fjust days after what happened with
OL,8,FMiller.
OL,10,FShe said: "I cried and I was like, 'I
OL,11,Fneed to speak for her now,' in the
OL,12,Fsense that this has happened to me.
OL,14,F"Poor Sarah didn't have a voice then.
OL,15,FMaybe if I came forward, I can stop
OL,16,Fanother officer doing the same.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
