OL,3,C'He's ruined any trust I have with
OL,4,Cpolice': Calls for better protection
OL,6,F"I know since I have come forward, I
OL,7,Fhave had sixty different men and women
OL,8,Fcome to me and tell me their story.
OL,9,FAnd a lot of them, I have helped them
OL,10,Fgo to the police now, but a lot of
OL,11,Fthem are still too scared because it's
OL,12,Fthe police versus them.
OL,14,F"So, if it takes me coming forward to
OL,15,Fhelp others, then that's what I am
OL,16,Fgonna do."
OL,18,FThe National Police Chiefs' Council
OL,19,F(NPCC) for all forces across the
OL,20,Fcountry declined to provide a
OL,21,Fstatement on this specific case.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
