OL,3,C'He's ruined any trust I have with
OL,4,Cpolice': Calls for better protection
OL,6,FHowever, they noted that following
OL,7,Frecommendations issued in 2024, in
OL,8,Flight of the Sarah Everard inquiry,
OL,9,Fforces have implemented stricter
OL,10,Fprotocols.
OL,12,FThese changes include the
OL,13,Freinstatement of face-to-face
OL,14,Finterviews and the use of integrity
OL,15,Fquestionnaires.
OL,17,FAdditionally, vetting procedures now
OL,18,Finclude mandatory Police National
OL,19,FDatabase (PND) checks, ensuring more
OL,20,Fconcrete measures are in place to
OL,21,Fscreen officers.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/12
